00:01:23.100 --> 00:01:26.150
So now let's talk
about our mission.

00:01:26.150 --> 00:01:30.260
Accessibility's mission
is integral to Google's.

00:01:30.260 --> 00:01:33.290
So integral it's in the
mission statement itself--

00:01:33.290 --> 00:01:35.510
to make the world's
information universally

00:01:35.510 --> 00:01:37.760
accessible and useful.

00:01:37.760 --> 00:01:41.410
Let's unpack that a little bit.

00:01:41.410 --> 00:01:45.850
Universally accessible means
everyone can use Android.

00:01:45.850 --> 00:01:48.670
We don't expect users to
adapt to our products.

00:01:48.670 --> 00:01:52.360
