barriers for anyone,

00:01:59.230 --> 00:02:00.650
we have more work to do.

00:02:00.650 --> 00:02:04.000
And it's with this mantra
that we design, build,

00:02:04.000 --> 00:02:07.990
and apply Google magic
to make both our products

00:02:07.990 --> 00:02:10.810
and the real world
around us more successful

00:02:10.810 --> 00:02:16.610
and more useful for more
users in more situations.

00:02:16.610 --> 00:02:19.790
The world's information
means it's not just

00:02:19.790 --> 00:02:21.890
about making what's on
the device accessible,

00:02:21.890 --> 00:02:25.340
but it's about making the
planet more accessible.

00:02:25.340 --> 00:02:29.270
And to do this, we apply
advances in machine learning

00:02:29.270 --> 00:02:33.170
and artificial intelligence--
what I call the Google magic--

00:02:33.170 --> 00:02:36.640
to meet the needs of
underserved communities.

00:02:36.640 --> 00:02:38.920
Last February, we
launched Live Transcribe,

00:02:38.920 --> 00:02:41.860
