00:02:44.850 --> 00:02:50.040
--anyone to have a
conversation without feedback.

00:02:50.040 --> 00:02:52.450
Allowing anyone to
have a conversation,

00:02:52.450 --> 00:02:54.210
even if they can't hear.

00:02:54.210 --> 00:02:57.960
You can think of Live
Transcribe as captioning

00:02:57.960 --> 00:02:59.640
for the real world.

00:02:59.640 --> 00:03:02.340
Sound Amplifier and
Lookout are also

00:03:02.340 --> 00:03:05.190
great examples of building
accessibility-first

00:03:05.190 --> 00:03:06.540
experiences.

00:03:06.540 --> 00:03:09.390
And you could think of
this overall approach

00:03:09.390 --> 00:03:12.750
as a practical,
useful, and potentially

00:03:12.750 --> 00:03:15.990
transformative application
