00:10:56.150 --> 00:10:57.910
So I can be in a
totally offline mode.

00:10:57.910 --> 00:10:59.080
I can be in a plane.

00:10:59.080 --> 00:10:59.980
It's going to work.

00:10:59.980 --> 00:11:03.160
Two, audio never
goes up to the cloud.

00:11:03.160 --> 00:11:05.190
So it just sits there locally.

00:11:05.190 --> 00:11:08.640
And best of all, developers
and content providers

00:11:08.640 --> 00:11:11.130
