00:11:15.250 --> 00:11:19.090
So with Live Caption, every
app, billions of videos,

00:11:19.090 --> 00:11:22.780
and podcasts from any
source are one step

00:11:22.780 --> 00:11:26.470
closer to being universally
accessible on Android.

